{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he wanted to reconnoiter exactly how he would be able, if any danger came, to go up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had already been in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "To go up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he kept a little suitcase packed at one door in his house, so that if they [INAUDIBLE] again on the door, on the front door, he told Fraulein-- Fraulein Annie had her instructions, and he would disappear out the back door with his packed little suitcase and would go into the schneekoppe and bounce down.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very athletic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, a trained-- mountain trainer-- trained man in the mountains, go down into Czechoslovakia and be free.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime, Hitler had taken Czechoslovakia, I believe, just about the-- shortly after we did our reconnoiter job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it wouldn't have done the poor man any good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, he realized that, to get up there and go down into Hitler's Czechoslovakia, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you know what ultimately happened to Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sachs?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned that-- I knew, of course, it must be true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I learned that because he was so prominent, he was a target man, among other things, for them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a-- you see, Hitler, I'm sure, had this marvelous dream for himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These rich Jews, I'll take all their ownings and their property, and I can run a wonderful war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There weren't that many Jews, and they didn't have that much money, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this was certainly one that they thought they could get a lot out of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took a lot out of them all with a big fine that Hitler leveraged right after this Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they took a great deal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they were after him.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
